title: Delicious Destiny
overview: Jae Yu Lee (Mike) is a chef of Western cuisine, who is obsessed with gourmet kitchen. While participating in a TV program on cooking, he meets playwright, Director sun Jia Min (Mao Xiao Tong), has an amazing sense of taste. From the very first meeting the young people disliked each other, but their passionate quarrels gradually originate attraction and the first feelings.
